+--------------------------------------------------------------------+

[0]coondoggie writes to tell us that top among feature requests for any
next-gen communications system among federal network managers is the
ability to [1]identify and notify employees in real time. "Federal
interest in presence technologies 'may come from the fact that agencies
want to know where their workforce is to be able to look at the
effectiveness and the efficiency of what they're able to do,' says Aaron
Heffron, vice president of Market Connections. 'They want to be in
contact with them at all times.'"

